- make checkheatlh script that will check if some bins are installed (like ag , fd, fzf)
  - nodejs
  - c11plus
- make delete via script (delete also cache dirs like .config)
  - ~/.local/share/nvim
  - ~/.local/state/nvim
- create wrapper script/make/mage files
  - e.g. that will wrap:
    - `install fzf`
    - `install kubectl`
    - .. 
    - `stow zsh`
- editorconfig

